Okay, I understand. I need to create a JSON array containing actions to operate accounting software. The actions should involve interacting with elements like account input fields, amount input fields, memo fields, and post/save buttons.

<OUTPUT_JSON>[{"action": "click", "selector": "input[name*=account i]", "text": ""}, {"action": "set_value", "selector": "input[name*=account i]", "text": "Checking Account"}, {"action": "click", "selector": "input[name*=amount i], input[type=number]", "text": ""}, {"action": "set_value", "selector": "input[name*=amount i], input[type=number]", "text": "100.00"}, {"action": "click", "selector": "textarea[name*=memo i]", "text": ""}, {"action": "set_value", "selector": "textarea[name*=memo i]", "text": "Deposit from customer"}, {"action": "click", "selector": "button:has-text(\"post\" i), button:has-text(\"save\" i)", "text": ""}]</OUTPUT_JSON>
